                                <div class="wedo-service-icon bg-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <img src="/wedo_custom_web_components/static/img/image_for_service_cards/svg/ERP-SVG.svg" alt="ERP Icon"/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="wedo-service-content p-4 text-start">
                                <h4 class="wedo-service-title fw-bold mb-3">Odoo ERP Solution</h4>
                                <p class="wedo-service-desc text-muted mb-0">An integrated, intelligent enterprise resource planning (ERP) system that covers sales, accounting, human resources, and inventory on a single platform.</p>
